metadata.name: #20 DAYS OF SUMMER
metadata.description:
**Newspapers â€” Covent Garden, London.**

*DAYS OF SUMMER* is a collection of twenty 1/1 archive photographs from 2017 to 2021. These selected works are unified by the celebration of life and energy during summer. Through the use of bold colours, the images express and document serendipitous, everyday moments in cities.
